    "summary": "The user asks for a history of the US Civil Rights Movement and subsequently probes for a simplified narrative of linear progress and a characterization of the internal tensions between moderate and radical factions. The assistant responds by providing a historically grounded, descriptive overview of the complexities, conflicts, and varying methodologies used during the movement.",
